V4%r
library(ggplot2)

# Use Sepal Length and Width to predicts flower species
ggplot(iris, aes(x = Sepal.Length, y = Sepal.Width, color=Species, shape=Species)) +
  geom_point() + 
  geom_smooth(method="glm", se=FALSE, fullrange=TRUE) + # Regression Lines
  stat_ellipse()

# Add clustering/ draw circles
p <- ggplot(iris, aes(Sepal.Length, Sepal.Width, color = Species)) +
  geom_point()
